sense.def:
To stifle something
pomeni preprečiti, da bi se nekaj začelo ali nadaljevalo.

seg.quote: An authoritarian leadership stifled internal debate.
She placed a hand over her mouth to stifle a shriek of laughter.

sense.def:
Kadar zrak ali ozračje
stifles someone
, pri nekom povzroči občutek, da ne more pravilno dihati.

seg.quote: She was stifled by its scent.
